    q: "How is this different from hiring a freelancer or agency?",
    a: "A freelancer writes 3–4 articles a month when they have time, charges $800–$1,200, and goes quiet when life happens. An agency charges $3,500–$5,000/month for 6–8 articles and a monthly report you have to decipher. Stacc publishes 30+ blog posts per month, automatically, every month, for $99. The math isn't close.",
